						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Date lost</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription consisting of six fragments appears to record some provisions made for conducting a festival ending with the <hi rend="italic">tīrtha</hi> on the day of Punarpūśam. It is engraved in characters of about the 16th century.</p>						

